# I Can't Believe It's Not Eurovision

This project is a mock Eurovision submission and voting app. Contestants role-play as countries, register entries, and vote through the website. The site also hosts a live-updating scoreboard that imitates a real Eurovision result flow.
Auth is handled by a different side on the same domain. We can leverage this via a shared sessions through Redis

This project is just a fun little side project for me and a few friends


### How to dev

- python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt
- python3 -m flask --app flaskr:create_app run --debug

You may want to set BASEPATH in library_eurovision.py to another directory to store the entries...


